1
00:01:22,960 --> 00:01:23,600
Come.

2
00:01:24,000 --> 00:01:24,800
Child.

3
00:01:26,960 --> 00:01:28,400
Drink. You drink first.

4
00:01:28,400 --> 00:01:29,840
Thank you.

5
00:01:30,280 --> 00:01:33,210
Drink up. I'll get you another bowl when you're done.

6
00:01:33,759 --> 00:01:35,280
Is it good?

7
00:01:36,400 --> 00:01:37,360
It is.

8
00:01:38,320 --> 00:01:39,120
Drink up.

9
00:01:39,520 --> 00:01:40,680
You haven't eaten for days.

10
00:01:40,680 --> 00:01:42,080
Have some more, quickly.

11
00:01:46,039 --> 00:01:46,360
Lord Fang.

12
00:01:46,360 --> 00:01:47,090
How did it go?

13
00:01:47,720 --> 00:01:48,880
I have completed the investigation.

14
00:01:48,880 --> 00:01:49,840
Regarding the Su family case from years ago,

15
00:01:49,840 --> 00:01:52,240
all the men of the Su family were executed on the spot,

16
00:01:52,240 --> 00:01:54,080
and the women were made government prostitutes.

17
00:01:54,080 --> 00:01:57,400
The eldest daughter of the Su family is indeed missing from the roster.

18
00:01:57,400 --> 00:01:58,560
Dismissed.

19
00:02:08,639 --> 00:02:09,500
Young Marquis.

20
00:02:09,800 --> 00:02:11,120
He fainted again.

21
00:02:11,640 --> 00:02:14,560
Why don't we stop the interrogation for today?

22
00:02:14,840 --> 00:02:17,520
The Imperial Preceptor has sent people to urge you several times,

23
00:02:17,520 --> 00:02:19,960
asking you to return home early to dine with him.

24
00:02:19,960 --> 00:02:21,840
And to discuss the case as well.

25
00:02:23,520 --> 00:02:25,240
Why does my father always nag me endlessly?

26
00:02:25,240 --> 00:02:26,360
He keeps rushing me.

27
00:02:26,360 --> 00:02:27,120
Go tell him,

28
00:02:27,400 --> 00:02:28,600
my interrogation here is more important.

29
00:02:28,600 --> 00:02:29,480
I won't go.

30
00:02:30,760 --> 00:02:33,820
I heard the Imperial Preceptor also invited Lord Fang.

31
00:02:33,960 --> 00:02:35,160
If you don't go,

32
00:02:35,320 --> 00:02:36,240
I'm afraid,

33
00:02:36,320 --> 00:02:40,520
Lord Fang will take the opportunity to badmouth you behind your back again.

34
00:02:41,320 --> 00:02:42,720
That Fang Ji.

35
00:02:44,640 --> 00:02:45,440
Let's go.

36
00:02:50,800 --> 00:02:52,130
Where is my waist token?

37
00:02:52,480 --> 00:02:54,320
Perhaps when you changed clothes upon entering,

38
00:02:54,320 --> 00:02:56,440
it got caught on the sash of your robe.

39
00:03:03,240 --> 00:03:03,920
Pihu.

40
00:03:04,840 --> 00:03:07,480
Notify the Dragon Shadow Guard to seal the city gates.

41
00:03:07,480 --> 00:03:09,000
Capture Gu Lihan.

42
00:03:09,440 --> 00:03:10,240
Yes, sir.

43
00:03:14,760 --> 00:03:15,080
Search every hideout!

44
00:03:15,080 --> 00:03:15,760
Secure the town! Find Gu!

45
00:03:15,760 --> 00:03:17,820
Report any leads to the Shadow Guard!

46
00:03:29,800 --> 00:03:32,060
Paying my respects to the Young Marquis.

47
00:03:35,440 --> 00:03:36,500
What are you doing?

48
00:03:38,280 --> 00:03:41,240
I didn't expect you to walk right into my trap.

49
00:03:44,720 --> 00:03:46,050
Where is my waist token?

50
00:03:46,400 --> 00:03:47,320
Waist token?

51
00:03:48,480 --> 00:03:49,760
What waist token?

52
00:03:50,920 --> 00:03:52,040
I have no idea.

53
00:03:54,840 --> 00:03:55,640
No matter.

54
00:03:56,600 --> 00:03:58,000
My favorite thing

55
00:03:58,640 --> 00:04:01,760
is interrogating shady people like you.

56
00:04:03,800 --> 00:04:04,760
Young Marquis.

57
00:04:05,400 --> 00:04:06,260
Young Marquis.

58
00:04:08,240 --> 00:04:10,600
Young Marquis, we've tried everything.

59
00:04:10,760 --> 00:04:12,760
But Huang Wansan is a tough nut to crack.

60
00:04:12,760 --> 00:04:14,490
He just won't give up any leads.

61
00:04:15,240 --> 00:04:16,440
Useless bunch.

62
00:04:18,240 --> 00:04:20,200
Of course he won't talk.

63
00:04:20,519 --> 00:04:21,920
As long as he keeps his mouth shut,

64
00:04:21,920 --> 00:04:23,250
you will keep him alive.

65
00:04:23,280 --> 00:04:24,680
But once he speaks,

66
00:04:25,000 --> 00:04:27,920
only death awaits him.

67
00:04:29,720 --> 00:04:32,360
Then what brilliant idea do you have, Miss Gu?

68
00:04:33,560 --> 00:04:35,840
I am willing to lend you a hand,

69
00:04:36,080 --> 00:04:37,340
to help solve the case.

70
00:04:43,159 --> 00:04:43,960
Speak.

71
00:04:44,280 --> 00:04:45,409
What are your terms?

72
00:04:49,600 --> 00:04:53,120
If I can find leads from Huang Wansan,

73
00:04:53,400 --> 00:04:55,280
you must let me go, Young Marquis.

74
00:04:56,159 --> 00:04:56,890
How about it?

75
00:05:02,600 --> 00:05:04,480
Young Marquis, have you given the instructions?

76
00:05:04,480 --> 00:05:05,840
Yes, I have.

77
00:05:07,720 --> 00:05:08,320
Go.

78
00:05:08,320 --> 00:05:09,200
Yes, sir.

79
00:05:09,440 --> 00:05:10,200
Wait.

80
00:05:11,680 --> 00:05:13,600
Make it look real.

81
00:05:14,360 --> 00:05:15,320
Yes.

82
00:05:30,200 --> 00:05:31,160
Huang Wansan.

83
00:05:32,440 --> 00:05:33,920
Since you entered the Imperial Prison,

84
00:05:33,920 --> 00:05:35,850
you haven't uttered a single word.

85
00:05:36,000 --> 00:05:38,130
The Master appreciates your loyalty,

86
00:05:38,200 --> 00:05:39,860
so he ordered me to rescue you.

87
00:05:40,600 --> 00:05:43,960
You think a cheap trick like this can fool me?

88
00:05:44,200 --> 00:05:46,440
I knew you wouldn't believe me.

89
00:05:47,320 --> 00:05:49,880
I'll take you to see someone first.

90
00:05:50,320 --> 00:05:51,120
Who?

91
00:06:00,040 --> 00:06:00,900
Spies reported

92
00:06:01,120 --> 00:06:03,920
that Miss Gu and a man resembling the Young Marquis

93
00:06:03,920 --> 00:06:05,180
entered Nanfeng Hall.

94
00:06:05,200 --> 00:06:07,120
She...

95
00:06:07,600 --> 00:06:08,560
What about her?

96
00:06:08,920 --> 00:06:11,760
She even threatened to order Nanfeng Hall's top attraction.

97
00:06:11,760 --> 00:06:12,560
Changfeng.

98
00:06:13,240 --> 00:06:14,240
Absurd.

99
00:06:48,400 --> 00:06:49,200
Changfeng.

100
00:06:53,520 --> 00:06:55,600
Changfeng, didn't you go to Jinzhou?

101
00:06:55,760 --> 00:06:56,960
Why are you back?

102
00:06:57,360 --> 00:06:58,560
Where are the others?

103
00:07:03,680 --> 00:07:04,940
You are not Changfeng.

104
00:07:15,800 --> 00:07:16,600
We're here.

105
00:07:19,760 --> 00:07:21,080
Why did you bring me here?

106
00:07:21,080 --> 00:07:21,560
To investigate.

107
00:07:21,560 --> 00:07:21,880
Hey.

108
00:07:22,920 --> 00:07:23,920
Investigate.

109
00:07:25,280 --> 00:07:26,480
If you want to investigate,

110
00:07:26,480 --> 00:07:28,120
why not interrogate in the Imperial Prison?

111
00:07:28,120 --> 00:07:30,380
Why bring me to this red-light district?

112
00:07:30,800 --> 00:07:33,240
Don't you know our laws are strict?

113
00:07:33,440 --> 00:07:35,240
Officials are forbidden from visiting prostitutes,

114
00:07:35,240 --> 00:07:36,760
let alone entering such venues.

115
00:07:36,760 --> 00:07:37,159
Yes.

116
00:07:38,240 --> 00:07:38,920
Oh my.

117
00:07:39,000 --> 00:07:39,960
Hurry up.

118
00:07:41,320 --> 00:07:43,880
Why are you tying me up?

119
00:07:43,960 --> 00:07:45,000
Let me go.

120
00:07:45,680 --> 00:07:46,960
Let me go.

121
00:07:50,120 --> 00:07:51,120
Untie me.

122
00:07:51,200 --> 00:07:52,200
Let me go. Shut up.

123
00:07:52,440 --> 00:07:53,040
Shut up.

124
00:07:57,080 --> 00:07:58,140
Why catch a gigolo?

125
00:07:58,400 --> 00:07:59,930
It's an emergency measure.

126
00:08:00,360 --> 00:08:01,890
All for the investigation.

127
00:08:03,400 --> 00:08:05,080
I found out earlier

128
00:08:05,440 --> 00:08:07,970
that Changfeng is Huang Wansan's confidant.

129
00:08:08,160 --> 00:08:09,880
If we start with him,

130
00:08:10,560 --> 00:08:13,020
Huang Wansan will take the bait more easily.

131
00:08:23,760 --> 00:08:24,560
Not bad.

132
00:08:25,400 --> 00:08:26,280
Really not bad.

133
00:08:27,240 --> 00:08:28,570
What are you muttering?

134
00:08:41,360 --> 00:08:44,560
These eyes and brows are truly handsome.

135
00:08:45,960 --> 00:08:47,120
With a little makeup,

136
00:08:47,120 --> 00:08:49,760
even the top courtesan of Qihong Tower would be put to shame.

137
00:08:49,760 --> 00:08:51,440
The Young Marquis's mother

138
00:08:52,000 --> 00:08:53,660
must be extremely beautiful.

139
00:09:00,200 --> 00:09:01,200
Are you done?

140
00:09:01,440 --> 00:09:02,200
Almost.

141
00:09:02,320 --> 00:09:04,180
Just need to finish the eyebrows.

142
00:09:05,120 --> 00:09:06,080
Young Marquis,

143
00:09:06,440 --> 00:09:09,160
if you fix that explosive temper of yours,

144
00:09:09,640 --> 00:09:10,640
the ladies chasing you

145
00:09:10,640 --> 00:09:11,960
would be lining up.

146
00:09:14,440 --> 00:09:15,240
Done.

147
00:09:21,240 --> 00:09:22,200
Absurd.

148
00:09:22,200 --> 00:09:24,400
Who let you paint me like this?

149
00:09:25,400 --> 00:09:28,000
Isn't this to interrogate Huang Wansan?

150
00:09:28,480 --> 00:09:29,320
Presumptuous.

151
00:09:29,320 --> 00:09:33,000
With that attitude, how will you serve guests?

152
00:09:36,240 --> 00:09:37,640
That's better.

153
00:09:40,840 --> 00:09:43,200
Alright, go interrogate Huang Wansan.

154
00:09:44,000 --> 00:09:44,800
No rush.

155
00:09:46,560 --> 00:09:48,720
Although the resemblance is close now,

156
00:09:48,720 --> 00:09:52,040
there are still differences up close.

157
00:09:52,640 --> 00:09:53,560
This drug

158
00:09:53,720 --> 00:09:56,040
can blur one's vision for four hours.

159
00:09:56,640 --> 00:09:58,040
He's become half-blind.

160
00:09:58,240 --> 00:10:00,100
That makes it easier for us to act.

161
00:10:11,120 --> 00:10:12,780
Great moves, Little Marquis.

162
00:10:14,360 --> 00:10:15,680
You dare deceive me?

163
00:10:37,800 --> 00:10:39,640
We didn't have time to identify the mastermind.

164
00:10:39,640 --> 00:10:40,640
In order to save you,

165
00:10:40,640 --> 00:10:42,100
all the leads were cut off.

166
00:10:43,360 --> 00:10:45,880
I reckon Huang Wansan doesn't know

167
00:10:45,880 --> 00:10:47,810
who the real mastermind is either.

168
00:10:48,440 --> 00:10:49,440
As for the rest,

169
00:10:49,560 --> 00:10:53,960
I'll have to trouble you, Little Marquis, to investigate in Jinzhou yourself.

170
00:11:04,000 --> 00:11:04,760
Father.

171
00:11:22,520 --> 00:11:23,850
What are you doing here?

172
00:11:26,040 --> 00:11:26,600
You disgrace.

173
00:11:26,600 --> 00:11:27,560
Stand up.

174
00:11:33,120 --> 00:11:35,120
Is that how you speak to your cousin?

175
00:11:35,520 --> 00:11:37,720
As a high-ranking court official,

176
00:11:38,160 --> 00:11:40,800
you went carousing at Nanfeng Pavilion,

177
00:11:41,080 --> 00:11:42,680
and even dressed as a gigolo.

178
00:11:43,000 --> 00:11:44,920
Have you no sense of decency?

179
00:11:45,200 --> 00:11:46,960
Is this how I taught you?

180
00:11:46,960 --> 00:11:49,080
To have such disregard for propriety?

181
00:11:49,080 --> 00:11:50,960
If Fang Ji hadn't come to tell me,

182
00:11:51,480 --> 00:11:54,280
I wouldn't have known what a scene you were making.

183
00:11:54,480 --> 00:11:56,320
You've always been biased, Father.

184
00:11:56,320 --> 00:11:58,680
I obviously went there to investigate a case.

185
00:11:58,680 --> 00:12:00,080
It is Fang Ji who is deceitful.

186
00:12:00,080 --> 00:12:01,340
He has ill intentions.

187
00:12:01,480 --> 00:12:03,320
My Dragon Shadow Guard works hard to investigate,

188
00:12:03,320 --> 00:12:05,050
yet he keeps getting in the way.

189
00:12:05,080 --> 00:12:07,280
You took my student to Nanfeng Pavilion.

190
00:12:07,280 --> 00:12:09,480
That is why I asked Teacher to come help.

191
00:12:11,040 --> 00:12:11,880
Investigate?

192
00:12:12,440 --> 00:12:14,120
Apart from torturing people into confessing,

193
00:12:14,120 --> 00:12:15,880
what do you know about investigating?

194
00:12:15,880 --> 00:12:16,320
I...

195
00:12:16,680 --> 00:12:18,160
I told you long ago

196
00:12:18,160 --> 00:12:19,480
to quit that job.

197
00:12:19,680 --> 00:12:20,960
What Dragon Shadow Guard?

198
00:12:20,960 --> 00:12:23,920
It's nothing but a glorified royal honor guard,

199
00:12:24,440 --> 00:12:27,560
full of pretty vases and attention-seeking fops.

200
00:12:28,680 --> 00:12:31,140
Grand Preceptor, may I be so bold as to speak?

201
00:12:31,880 --> 00:12:34,720
The Dragon Shadow Guard was indeed formerly the Imperial Guard,

202
00:12:34,720 --> 00:12:38,240
but it now has a pacification office dedicated to criminal cases.

203
00:12:38,240 --> 00:12:40,160
The Little Marquis, for his meritorious service in investigations,

204
00:12:40,160 --> 00:12:41,420
was granted his title.

205
00:12:41,640 --> 00:12:44,120
Investigating this case was by order of His Majesty.

206
00:12:44,120 --> 00:12:44,920
It is his duty.

207
00:12:46,200 --> 00:12:47,240
The Little Marquis

208
00:12:47,240 --> 00:12:50,360
is absolutely not the 'pretty vase' you described.

209
00:12:51,640 --> 00:12:52,440
Furthermore,

210
00:12:52,720 --> 00:12:53,320
Lord Fang,

211
00:12:53,840 --> 00:12:56,840
going to Nanfeng Pavilion was not the Little Marquis's idea.

212
00:12:56,840 --> 00:12:57,920
It was my idea.

213
00:12:58,000 --> 00:13:00,160
I insisted on dragging the Little Marquis along.

214
00:13:00,160 --> 00:13:03,120
Though the Little Marquis was unwilling to visit such a filthy place,

215
00:13:03,120 --> 00:13:04,880
he had no choice for the sake of the case,

216
00:13:04,880 --> 00:13:07,200
and had to risk his personal safety.

217
00:13:09,040 --> 00:13:12,640
You have a sharp tongue, girl.

218
00:13:13,880 --> 00:13:15,080
You look unfamiliar.

219
00:13:15,880 --> 00:13:20,120
How did you end up with the Little Marquis?

220
00:13:21,360 --> 00:13:22,440
Grand Preceptor,

221
00:13:22,760 --> 00:13:24,360
I am Gu Lihan.

222
00:13:24,680 --> 00:13:26,360
Though I am but a woman,

223
00:13:26,760 --> 00:13:28,760
I am familiar with the ways of the martial world.

224
00:13:28,760 --> 00:13:30,520
I was fortunate to be appreciated by Lord Fang

225
00:13:30,520 --> 00:13:32,440
and recruited as his advisor.

226
00:13:32,720 --> 00:13:35,600
Now I have been recommended to serve in the Dragon Shadow Guard.

227
00:13:35,600 --> 00:13:37,440
If Fang Ji recommended you,

228
00:13:38,240 --> 00:13:41,120
then Miss Gu must be very capable.

229
00:13:41,280 --> 00:13:42,960
But Rui,

230
00:13:43,080 --> 00:13:47,160
I'm surprised you accepted someone recommended by your cousin.

231
00:13:48,320 --> 00:13:48,840
Yes.

232
00:13:48,960 --> 00:13:50,600
I made a bet with Fang Ji,

233
00:13:50,720 --> 00:13:52,840
and won her from him.

234
00:13:55,520 --> 00:13:57,640
Ji and Rui were recruiting talent,

235
00:13:57,720 --> 00:13:59,960
and both spotted Miss Gu's abilities,

236
00:14:00,320 --> 00:14:01,920
which led to this situation.

237
00:14:02,840 --> 00:14:05,900
What use does the Dragon Shadow Guard have for scribes?

238
00:14:06,240 --> 00:14:10,600
Isn't this just ruining Miss Gu's future?

239
00:14:11,440 --> 00:14:13,960
It is precisely because the Dragon Shadow Guards are military officers

240
00:14:13,960 --> 00:14:16,720
that we need civil clerks to assist.

241
00:14:16,840 --> 00:14:17,880
Never mind.

242
00:14:19,120 --> 00:14:20,180
It's getting late.

243
00:14:20,440 --> 00:14:22,120
You should go back and rest.

244
00:14:23,120 --> 00:14:25,960
We'll discuss other matters tomorrow.

245
00:14:35,000 --> 00:14:36,330
I'll take my leave then.

246
00:14:46,760 --> 00:14:47,560
Miss Gu.

247
00:14:50,640 --> 00:14:52,360
What is it now, Lord Fang?

248
00:14:52,440 --> 00:14:54,370
I'll have someone escort you home.

249
00:14:57,240 --> 00:14:59,700
I'll have someone take you to the guest room.

250
00:15:00,760 --> 00:15:03,120
No need. I won't bother you two.

251
00:15:03,160 --> 00:15:04,960
I have legs. I can walk by myself.

252
00:15:20,800 --> 00:15:21,660
Young Marquis.

253
00:15:42,120 --> 00:15:42,920
My Lord.

254
00:15:43,120 --> 00:15:44,920
What are they whispering about so secretively?
